item.title: RSBot back?
item.dc:creator: @bloodrayne bloodrayne
item.description:
@bloodrayne wrote:

They get our e-mails from scraping forums like this, and two personal e-mails have been posted in this thread alone

I’m sure they also use e-mails from stolen databases as well

I frequently Google my personal e-mail with quotes around it and if I find my e-mail publicly available anywhere(usually forums), I contact whoever I need to to remove it.

Right now, this is the only place I’ve been able to find my e-mail: http://goo.gl/Lp4ES

I wouldn’t be surprised if some of you are on there, it was stolen from a rather large website
